5C2d</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/239_11.5.0.xml#_d51fb770-84da-40fa-bb93-b08e4fc7a464" id="_c830e2fd-219c-4044-acab-11362ea9530d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2e</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/240_12.6.0.xml#_d8e14281-fd9b-4d91-94b4-5c974f26612d" id="_ac05a807-9364-4794-bcfc-6f2f2276b196" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2f</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/241_12.4.0.xml#_b99593e5-fc68-426f-807d-594100be985f" id="_f3f1e787-8e2e-4ddf-9c40-f35f07cfdfaa" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2g</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/242_12.4.0.xml#_6ecc85f0-19de-408a-830c-abe2db9b15e9" id="_22b69ce3-2f46-495c-9c3b-5f79bc5ae4e1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2h</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/298_12.4.0.xml#_9d449705-1791-444b-a2b4-bfc9ef485e67" id="_96b3c8f1-8266-4972-905f-a5b6935a44c7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2i</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/299_12.6.0.xml#_d40c07f0-9acb-42cb-ace2-7ebda767de38" id="_eaed37e6-3e42-480e-907d-1a3876bc0627" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2j</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/300_12.7.0.xml#_3475a9a2-45c7-4bb3-8066-1f956ab26747" id="_e8386271-b691-4690-8c82-310ca5fd8bbc" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2k</xref>; and</li><li id="_d763a06b-4644-42bb-a2b7-1dc742915544">the internal heat gains in a building—<ol><li>from occupants and hot meals, in accordance with one of the options in <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/306_12.1.0.xml#_7d319f4b-75b5-4a1f-9f5d-f05d21195931" id="_c478ecba-b1ab-400a-b48d-65578e663494" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table S35C2n</xref>; and</li><li>from appliances and equipment, in accordance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/301_12.1.0.xml#_7dad389f-a0e9-42bb-ad33-9ac62783bbda" id="_29b632cc-cc00-487c-96a4-43c88fc232e5" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table S35C2l</xref>; and</li><li>from artificial lighting, determined in accordance with (2).</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_ae7d4e2d-e49b-4d38-a9f1-34eb5a8adbed" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_bf0e98e3-f8cc-4d15-aed9-97aa38a3a1d9">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The artificial lighting, must be modelled on the basis of the proposed level of artificial lighting in the building with the daily profile in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/236_11.5.0.xml#_7ee35644-909b-4fd7-a34c-62f32dfc666d" id="_42be9169-add9-4522-ac0d-092502175f1e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Tables S35C2b</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/237_11.6.0.xml#_6cdb33f3-7b1f-4b51-9791-4739e4392562" id="_45eb481c-35cc-4718-a9c6-5d621e326f83" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">S35C2c</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/23